How is it my fault?

1063
01:12:59,229 --> 01:13:02,253
That ball you sold them.
The signature was fake.

1064
01:13:04,789 --> 01:13:07,931
The things you do for
yourself hurt other people.

1065
01:13:07,932 --> 01:13:10,115
Yeah I know I heard that before.

1066
